The paper deals with personalized image tagging, which involves information retrieval (IR) and computer vision (CV) techniques. The authors also propose a machine learning approach, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to deal with user-generated tags, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (CL). Finally, the paper deals with multimedia (MM) data, which is another relevant sub-category.
